txt.en: Due to your continued assistance across An Shêru you are now well-acquainted with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Your continued efforts to support An Shêru earns you greater favour with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Acquaintance of the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
